      "body" : "@MustafaG&#252;ven I had the same problem as you, where my <code>ImageView</code> disappears. The trick is to make the layout part (i.e., <code>&lt;this_part_here&gt;.LayoutParams</code>) be the same as what the parent of the <code>ImageView</code> is. So, for example, if you&#39;ve placed your <code>ImageView</code> within a <code>TableRow</code> within a <code>TableLayout</code>, you should have it as <code>TableRow.LayoutParams</code>."
