    "body" : "<p>Simply create a LayoutParams object and assign it to your imageView</p>\n\n<pre><code>LinearLayout.LayoutParams params = new LinearLayout.LayoutParams(150, 150);\nimageView.setLayoutParams(params);\n</code></pre>\n"
