    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I have played this one with <code>pixel</code> and <code>dp</code>.</p>\n\n<pre><code>private int dimensionInPixel = 200;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>How to set by <strong>pixel</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>view.getLayoutParams().height = dimensionInPixel;\nview.getLayoutParams().width = dimensionInPixel;\nview.requestLayout();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>How to set by <strong>dp</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int dimensionInDp = (int) TypedValue.applyDimension(TypedValue.COMPLEX_UNIT_DIP, dimensionInPixel, getResources().getDisplayMetrics());\nview.getLayoutParams().height = dimensionInDp;\nview.getLayoutParams().width = dimensionInDp;\nview.requestLayout();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Hope this would help you.</p>\n"
