    "body" : "<p>You can set value for all case.</p>\n\n<pre><code>demoImage.getLayoutParams().height = 150;\n\ndemoImage.getLayoutParams().width = 150;\n\ndemoImage.setScaleType(ImageView.ScaleType.FIT_XY);\n</code></pre>\n"
