    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In the scenario where the widget size needs to be set programmatically, ensure the below rules.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Set <code>LayoutParam</code> <strong>for the Layout in which you are adding that view</strong>. In my case I am adding to <code>TableRow</code> so I had to do <code>TableRow.LayoutParams</code></li>\n<li>Follow this code</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><code>final float scale = getResources().getDisplayMetrics().density;\n                int dpWidthInPx  = (int) (17 * scale);\n                int dpHeightInPx = (int) (17 * scale);</code></p>\n\n<p><code>TableRow.LayoutParams deletelayoutParams = new TableRow.LayoutParams(dpWidthInPx, dpHeightInPx);\n                button.setLayoutParams(deletelayoutParams);\ntableRow.addView(button, 1);</code></p>\n"
