    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you want to just fit the image in image view you can use\" wrap content\" in height and width property with scale-type but if you want to set manually you have to use LayoutParams.</p>\n\n<p>Layoutparams is efficient for setting the layout height and width programmatically. </p>\n"
