    "question_id" : 3144940,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In order to set the ImageView and Height Programatically, you can do</p>\n\n<pre><code>            //Makesure you calculate the density pixel and multiply it with the size of width/height\n            float dpCalculation = getResources().getDisplayMetrics().density;\n            your_imageview.getLayoutParams().width = (int) (150 * dpCalculation);\n\n            //Set ScaleType according to your choice...\n            your_imageview.setScaleType(ImageView.ScaleType.CENTER_CROP);\n</code></pre>\n"
